        <PartOf>multimedia.audio</PartOf>
        <Summary xml:lang="en">Terminal music player</Summary>
        <Description xml:lang="en">kew is a terminal music player with themes and cover-derived colors,
lyrics support (.lrc, SYLT, Vorbis comments), MPRIS desktop integration,
and support for MP3, FLAC, M4A/AAC, Opus, Ogg, WebM and WAV. It can search
and browse your library with gapless playback, playlist editing, and a
visualizer. Album art can be shown in sixel-capable terminals via Chafa.
</Description>
